Okay. Good.

869
00:37:12,300 --> 00:37:12,940
Great.

870
00:37:15,420 --> 00:37:16,150
Take a break.

871
00:37:21,150 --> 00:37:23,440
About the money lost last time,

872
00:37:23,510 --> 00:37:24,620
how is that going?

873
00:37:25,760 --> 00:37:26,760
We're still selling

874
00:37:26,760 --> 00:37:27,980
the leftover clothes.

875
00:37:27,980 --> 00:37:29,510
We should have some money
by the end of the month.

876
00:37:29,510 --> 00:37:31,170
I'll pay you as soon as I get it.

877
00:37:32,460 --> 00:37:34,660
I have to wait until the end of the month?

878
00:37:36,500 --> 00:37:37,510
Mr. Zheng, I...

879
00:37:39,550 --> 00:37:40,070
Okay.

880
00:37:40,690 --> 00:37:41,550
Let's see

881
00:37:41,550 --> 00:37:42,730
Page 12.

882
00:37:42,780 --> 00:37:44,090
Page 12.

883
00:37:48,130 --> 00:37:48,990
Zhuang Zhuang.

884
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:55,860
I had more classes
this month than last month.

885
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:58,410
Take this to tide you over.

886
00:37:59,190 --> 00:37:59,590
Here.

887
00:37:59,590 --> 00:38:00,750
This isn't appropriate, Mr. Zheng.

888
00:38:00,750 --> 00:38:02,320
What's inappropriate?

889
00:38:02,510 --> 00:38:04,190
Just consider it doing me a favor.

890
00:38:04,190 --> 00:38:05,450
Take it to my wife.

891
00:38:06,840 --> 00:38:07,570
I can't.

892
00:38:08,360 --> 00:38:09,490
Don't say no.

893
00:38:09,590 --> 00:38:10,690
If you don't,

894
00:38:10,760 --> 00:38:13,100
I'm really done for.

895
00:38:16,260 --> 00:38:17,070
Hurry, hurry.

896
00:38:23,010 --> 00:38:23,670
Zhuang Zhuang,

897
00:38:23,670 --> 00:38:24,800
did you earn all this

898
00:38:25,070 --> 00:38:26,640
from selling clothes?

899
00:38:26,860 --> 00:38:27,990
That was fast.

900
00:38:29,090 --> 00:38:29,940
I wish I had a daughter

901
00:38:29,940 --> 00:38:31,170
like you.

902
00:38:31,900 --> 00:38:33,030
I made steamed buns today.

903
00:38:33,030 --> 00:38:34,560
Come try some after class.

904
00:38:35,510 --> 00:38:37,460
Mrs. Zheng, actually...

905
00:38:37,530 --> 00:38:38,390
Zhuang Zhuang.

906
00:38:39,300 --> 00:38:40,500
Break is over.

907
00:38:40,610 --> 00:38:41,560
Time for class.

908
00:38:41,880 --> 00:38:43,210
I know. Stop rushing us.

909
00:38:43,210 --> 00:38:44,740
Can't we just chat for a bit?

910
00:38:46,510 --> 00:38:48,010
Zhuang Zhuang, hurry up and go to class.

911
00:38:48,010 --> 00:38:49,410
Mr. Zheng is rushing you.

912
00:38:49,500 --> 00:38:50,090
Hurry up.

913
00:38:51,820 --> 00:38:52,530
Good luck.

914
00:39:36,550 --> 00:39:39,170
I went for a makeup test a while ago.

915
00:39:39,500 --> 00:39:41,760
I ran into Mr. Xu in the neighboring crew.

916
00:39:41,920 --> 00:39:43,950
He was eating alone in a corner.

917
00:39:43,980 --> 00:39:45,310
He looked so miserable.

918
00:39:56,940 --> 00:39:57,570
Zongbao.

919
00:39:58,230 --> 00:39:59,110
What's wrong with you?

920
00:39:58,470 --> 00:39:59,730
[Registration Room]

921
00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:03,090
Acting is hard on the back.

922
00:40:03,120 --> 00:40:04,490
For veteran actors,

923
00:40:04,550 --> 00:40:06,590
eight out of ten

924
00:40:06,730 --> 00:40:08,120
have bad backs.

925
00:40:08,590 --> 00:40:10,250
Didn't you go to the hospital?

926
00:40:10,630 --> 00:40:11,740
Why waste that money?

927
00:40:11,740 --> 00:40:12,820
It'll heal with some rest.

928
00:40:12,820 --> 00:40:14,130
[Registration Room]

929
00:40:13,210 --> 00:40:14,010
Wait a second.

930
00:40:14,340 --> 00:40:14,760
What?

931
00:40:16,530 --> 00:40:17,660
Come inside with me.

932
00:40:18,110 --> 00:40:19,070
What do you want?

933
00:40:19,260 --> 00:40:19,990
To fix you up.

934
00:40:20,500 --> 00:40:20,880
What?

935
00:40:26,710 --> 00:40:27,370
Feels good.

936
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:33,050
Keep it down.

937
00:40:33,260 --> 00:40:35,090
People will think I did something to you.

938
00:40:35,090 --> 00:40:35,480
What?

939
00:40:36,940 --> 00:40:38,200
Out of a white dye vat,

940
00:40:38,300 --> 00:40:40,330
can you get black cloth?

941
00:40:41,000 --> 00:40:43,380
Right here. Right here.

942
00:40:44,360 --> 00:40:44,900
Done.

943
00:40:47,550 --> 00:40:48,700
Get up. Move around.

944
00:40:49,010 --> 00:40:49,940
See how it feels.

945
00:40:54,510 --> 00:40:55,580
You know what?

946
00:40:56,230 --> 00:40:57,450
I do feel

947
00:40:57,600 --> 00:40:58,690
much lighter.

948
00:41:00,360 --> 00:41:01,120
Zongbao.

949
00:41:02,070 --> 00:41:03,640
The roles you play every day

950
00:41:03,690 --> 00:41:05,420
are quite varied, aren't they?

951
00:41:06,230 --> 00:41:08,130
Well, being an actor is about

952
00:41:08,390 --> 00:41:11,620
playing all kinds of characters.

953
00:41:13,480 --> 00:41:15,890
So, do laborers earn more,

954
00:41:16,190 --> 00:41:17,590
or do handymen earn more?

955
00:41:21,070 --> 00:41:21,870
I'm not picky.

956
00:41:22,490 --> 00:41:23,620
I'll play anything.

957
00:41:24,280 --> 00:41:25,880
Just trying to make a living.

958
00:41:32,890 --> 00:41:36,000
You're still not done with your work?

959
00:41:38,420 --> 00:41:39,280
Go to sleep.

960
00:41:40,280 --> 00:41:42,790
Health is your greatest asset.

961
00:41:48,030 --> 00:41:49,060
This girl

962
00:41:49,630 --> 00:41:50,490
is really dumb.

963
00:41:52,730 --> 00:41:54,500
That's where you don't get it.

964
00:41:55,420 --> 00:41:56,790
She may seem a bit

965
00:41:56,900 --> 00:41:58,370
dumb in this scene,

966
00:41:58,800 --> 00:41:59,860
but actually,

967
00:41:59,900 --> 00:42:01,880
the director wants to use this scene

968
00:42:01,880 --> 00:42:03,010
to see if the actress

969
00:42:03,150 --> 00:42:04,050
can perceive that

970
00:42:04,050 --> 00:42:05,710
she's actually playing dumb.

971
00:42:05,980 --> 00:42:07,360
If you act like she's really stupid,

972
00:42:07,360 --> 00:42:08,290
then it's wrong.

973
00:42:08,460 --> 00:42:09,790
There's a lot more to it.

974
00:42:14,940 --> 00:42:15,940
Crap. Crap. Crap.

975
00:42:45,210 --> 00:42:46,010
Who is this...

976
00:42:46,530 --> 00:42:48,190
kind person?
